00:09:04.060 --> 00:09:06.854
to revolutionize personalized pharmaceuticals.
客制化药品的潜力。

155
00:09:07.606 --> 00:09:10.900
Today, taking medicine is, to some degree, trial and error.
今天，服药在某种程度上 是一种试错法。

156
00:09:10.943 --> 00:09:13.737
You don't really know if the drug is going to work for you
你并不确切知道这个药物 是不是对你有效，

157
00:09:13.779 --> 00:09:15.655
until you put it in your body.
直到把它服入体内。

158
00:09:16.115 --> 00:09:22.955
But what if we had a miniature human replica of you with your cells --
但如果我们有一个里面 有你细胞的微型人体复制品，

159
00:09:23.871 --> 00:09:29.252
eye cells, brain cells, heart cells, muscle cells, blood cells --
——眼睛细胞、大脑细胞、心脏细胞、 肌肉细胞、血液细胞——

160
00:09:29.252 --> 00:09:30.588
on a chip?
在一个芯片上。

161
00:09:31.588 --> 00:09:34.465
A miniature human replica of you.
你的微型人体复制品。

162
00:09:35.049 --> 00:09:38.386
We could take the drugs, test them on the cells in the lab first
我们可以测试药物，首先在实验室里 在细胞上测试它们

163
00:09:38.429 --> 00:09:39.597
to see how it works.
看是否有效。

164
00:09:39.597 --> 00:09:42.348
If it works, fantastic. Go ahead and take the drug.
如果有效，那很好。 下一步就是服药。

165
00:09:42.348 --> 00:09:47.061
If it doesn't, pharmacists can order up custom drugs just for you.
如果无效，药剂师可以为你定制药物。

166
00:09:49.022 --> 00:09:53.109
This has been the hope and dream of scientists for decades.
这是科学家数十年来的希望和梦想。

167
00:09:53.943 --> 00:09:55.570
With this technology,
通过这种技术，

168
00:09:55.570 --> 00:10:00.033
we can finally realize the true potential of stem cells:
我们可以最终实现干细胞的真正潜力：

169
00:10:00.074 --> 00:10:04.996
on-demand functional cures made from your cells.
来自你的细胞的按需功能治疗方法。

170
00:10:05.831 --> 00:10:08.542
Cures that your body won't reject.
你的身体不会排斥的治疗方法。

171
00:10:08.583 --> 00:10:11.962
Cures that truly work for everyone.
真正适合每个人的治疗方法。

172
00:10:15.131 --> 00:10:21.512
The future of regenerative medicine is 100 percent personalized,
未来的再生医学100%是客制化的，

173
00:10:21.554 --> 00:10:24.516
and it's a lot closer than you think.
这比你想象的要近得多。

174
00:10:24.558 --> 00:10:25.768
Thank you.
谢谢。

175
00:10:26.352 --> 00:10:29.520
(Applause)
（鼓掌）